  <motion chara="097" action="move" pos="120,0" duration="30"></motion>
  <motion chara="100" action="move" pos="0,-50" duration="30"></motion>
  <delay t="1"></delay>
  <text>
    <p>Their objective is the old sword 「Hekihan」.[\s]</p>
    <p>The one who gets it wins, and the ones that can't die.</p>
  </text>
  <mono chara="002">
    <p></p>
    <p>（...You're going to help me, right?）</p>
  </mono>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>I completely let my instincts control the movement of her body.</p>
    <p>「A girl.」's Li Sushang consciousness murmured.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono chara="002" pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>「You're my sword...」</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="3"></event>
  <motion chara="100" action="move" pos="-25,100" duration="30"></motion>
  <motion chara="096" action="move" pos="-100,0" duration="30"></motion>
  <motion chara="097" action="move" pos="50,0" duration="30"></motion>
  <delay t="3"></delay>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>The kenjou reached its highest position and stopped for a moment, then immediately fell.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>Suddenly, a very nostalgic feeling welled up inside Li Sushang.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>Have I seen this before?[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Why is the sword falling in front of me so friendly?[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>…………</p>
    <p>Years ago.</p>
    <p>…………</p>
  </mono>
