  <text>
    <p>My fingers moved closer to the hilt of my sword.</p>
    <p>It was as if the sound of clashing swords rang in her head.</p>
    <p>At that very moment, Li Sushang was convinced she had mastered 「Ken'i」.</p>
  </text>
  <transition mode="dissolve" in="0.5" stop="0.5" out="1" color="#000000"></transition>
