  <motion chara="097" action="hide"></motion>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <text>However, it wasn’t she who gripped the hilt of her sword</text>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="0.8"></event>
  <motion chara="096" action="show" pos="0,-1080" img="老鹰-特写-狞笑（带血）"></motion>
  <delay t="0.1"></delay>
  <motion chara="096" action="move" pos="center" duration="0.3"></motion>
  <delay t="0.3"></delay>
  <dialog chara="015">「I won!」</dialog>
  <text>What reached my ears were words declaring death.</text>
  <dialog chara="015">「Die, girl-」</dialog>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="1"></event>
  <motion chara="097" action="show" pos="center" img="李素裳-特写-濒死" duration="1"></motion>
  <delay t="1"></delay>
  <dialog chara="002">「......」</dialog>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="2"></event>
  <cg duration="2"></cg>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>The despair and disappointment at this moment was greater than ever before.[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>The girl is not afraid to die.[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>However, he had gained hope and lost it. He’d experienced the agony of climbing up to a peak before falling down</p>
    <p>Along with a great regret that seemed to sink into my body.</p>
    <p>The screams and trembling never ceased.</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="1"></event>
  <motion chara="097" action="img_trans" img="李素裳-特写-坚定" duration="1"></motion>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>「—No!」</p>
  </mono>
