  <text>
    <p>The next moment, even if she was about to be cut in half with a single slash...</p>
    <p>My instincts refused to admit defeat.</p>
  </text>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="1"></event>
  <cg duration="0.5" origin="99%,10%" img="CG_第一折_抢剑_鹰挥刀"></cg>
  <delay t="0.5"></delay>
  <text>
    <p>Her extremely hazy consciousness pushed out her bare palm sword</p>
    <p>He desperately attacked the enemy, intending to strike a mutual blow.</p>
  </text>
  <cg duration="5"></cg>
  <text>
    <p>In this moment, the girl who understood and accepted 「Death.」...</p>
    <p>Finally, one step too late...</p>
  </text>
  <text>「Prepare yourself.」.</text>
